aVNow picture the stadium last year
p31
aVat the world championships of the 100 meters:
p32
aVthousands of fans waiting with baited breath
p33
aVto see Usain Bolt, the fastest man in history;
p34
aVflashbulbs popping as the nine fastest men in the world
p35
aVcoil themselves into their blocks.
p36
aVAnd I want you to pretend
p37
aVthat Jesse Owens is in that race.
